---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<BaseHead 
		title={`Understanding NZ Privacy & Security Requirements | Practical Compliance Help`} 
		description="Plain language guidance on New Zealand's Privacy Act, NZISM, and security requirements. We help Kiwis understand and meet compliance needs without unnecessary complexity."
		keywords="NZ Privacy Act, NZISM explained, PSR compliance NZ, New Zealand security requirements, privacy law New Zealand, practical compliance NZ"
	/>
</head>
<body>
	<a href="#main-content" class="skip-to-main">Skip to main content</a>
	<Header />
	<main id="main-content">
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>Understanding NZ Security Requirements</h1>
				<p class="tagline">Making New Zealand's privacy and security frameworks accessible</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<p>New Zealand has specific privacy laws and security frameworks that can be confusing to navigate. We help individuals and businesses understand what these mean in practical terms and implement appropriate protection measures without unnecessary complexity.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Key Security Frameworks</h2>
				
				<div class="grid grid-3">
					<div class="card">
						<h3>NZISM</h3>
						<p>The government's comprehensive manual for protecting official information. It outlines security controls, risk management approaches, and technical requirements for government agencies and their partners.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Protective Security Requirements</h3>
						<p>An all-of-government framework covering personnel, physical, and information security measures for protecting sensitive government information.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="card">
						<h3>International Standards</h3>
						<p>Various international standards and certifications recognized within New Zealand security frameworks, including FIPS 140-3, Common Criteria, and other validation programs.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>How We Help</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-3">
					<div class="feature-card">
						<h3>Plain Language Guidance</h3>
						<p>We explain NZISM, PSR, Privacy Act, and other requirements in straightforward terms, helping you understand what actually applies to your situation.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<h3>Practical Solutions</h3>
						<p>We identify products and practices that meet compliance requirements while fitting your budget and operational reality.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<h3>Implementation Support</h3>
						<p>We help you implement security measures that work in New Zealand's context, with realistic timelines and costs.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="disclaimer">
					<h3>Important Information</h3>
					<p><strong>Hermetrix provides advisory services and implementation support for security solutions.</strong> We are not a government agency and cannot provide official compliance certifications or security clearances.</p>
					<p>Formal compliance status, security accreditations, and government approvals must be obtained through the appropriate official channels. We support your journey toward compliance through education and appropriate solution implementation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container text-center">
				<h2>Ready for Strategic OPSEC Assessment?</h2>
				<p>Contact us to discuss how intelligence-driven OPSEC analysis can enhance your compliance and security posture.</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="/services" class="btn primary">Our Services</a>
					<a href="mailto:hello@hermetrix.nz" class="btn secondary">Contact Us</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	<Footer />

	<style>
		.hero {
			padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
		}

		.tagline {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			color: var(--text-secondary);
			margin-top: var(--space-md);
			font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		}

		.card {
			background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
			backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
		}

		.feature-card {
			padding: var(--space-xl);
			border: 2px solid var(--white);
			border-radius: 6px;
			background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
			backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
			box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			position: relative;
			overflow: hidden;
		}

		.feature-card::before {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			top: 50%;
			left: 50%;
			width: 0;
			height: 0;
			border-radius: 50%;
			background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--cyan) 0%, transparent 70%);
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
			transition: all 0.5s ease;
			z-index: 0;
		}

		.feature-card:hover {
			border-color: var(--accent-secondary);
			transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
			box-shadow: 7px 7px 0 rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
		}

		.feature-card:hover::before {
			width: 200%;
			height: 200%;
			opacity: 0.05;
		}

		.feature-card h3 {
			color: var(--accent-secondary);
			margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
			font-weight: 900;
			position: relative;
			z-index: 1;
		}

		.feature-card p {
			margin: 0;
			color: var(--text-secondary);
			position: relative;
			z-index: 1;
		}

		.disclaimer {
			padding: var(--space-2xl);
			background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
			backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
			border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-primary);
			border-radius: 6px;
			box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.2);
			position: relative;
		}

		.disclaimer::before {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			left: -5px;
			top: 0;
			width: 5px;
			height: 0;
			background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--magenta), var(--cyan), var(--electric-blue));
			transition: height 0.6s ease;
		}

		.disclaimer:hover::before {
			height: 100%;
		}

		.disclaimer h3 {
			color: var(--accent-primary);
			margin-top: 0;
			font-weight: 900;
		}

		.disclaimer p {
			margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
			color: var(--text-secondary);
		}

		.disclaimer p:last-child {
			margin-bottom: 0;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			display: flex;
			gap: var(--space-lg);
			justify-content: center;
			margin-top: var(--space-xl);
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.hero {
				padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
			}

			.tagline {
				font-size: 1rem;
			}

			.grid-3 {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				gap: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.card {
				padding: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.feature-card {
				padding: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.feature-card:hover {
				transform: translate(-1px, -1px);
				box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
			}

			.disclaimer {
				padding: var(--space-lg);
				border-left-width: 4px;
			}

			.cta-buttons {
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: stretch;
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 480px) {
			.hero {
				padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
			}

			.card {
				padding: var(--space-md);
				border-width: 2px;
			}

			.feature-card {
				padding: var(--space-md);
				border-width: 2px;
			}

			.disclaimer {
				padding: var(--space-md);
				border-left-width: 3px;
			}

			.disclaimer h3 {
				font-size: 1.125rem;
			}

			.disclaimer p {
				font-size: 0.875rem;
			}
		}
	</style>
</body>
</html>
